00:26:19.280 --> 00:26:20.840 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:26:20.840 --> 00:26:25.130 align:middle line:84%
How about when you're in
the solar system of these--

00:26:25.130 --> 00:26:29.030 align:middle line:84%
visiting on these
contract jobs, and you

