>> You mean like
in space to space?

00:26:37.980 --> 00:26:38.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:26:38.780 --> 00:26:40.370 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yeah, absolutely.

00:26:40.370 --> 00:26:43.520 align:middle line:84%
We've gotten to broad
sites, boarding parties.

00:26:43.520 --> 00:26:44.880 align:middle line:90%
I mean, yeah, it can happen.

00:26:44.880 --> 00:26:46.053 align:middle line:90%
It can get really hairy.

00:26:46.053 --> 00:26:46.970 align:middle line:90%
It can totally happen.

00:26:46.970 --> 00:26:50.300 align:middle line:84%
>> So you've had firefights
using these weapons

00:26:50.300 --> 00:26:51.890 align:middle line:90%
on your craft?

00:26:51.890 --> 00:26:53.180 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, absolutely.

00:26:53.180 --> 00:26:53.980 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:26:53.980 --> 00:26:57.050 align:middle line:84%
>> And how does this not
damage the hull of the craft?

00:26:57.050 --> 00:27:00.080 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I'm not
