00:27:14.960 --> 00:27:17.070 align:middle line:90%
but it happens.

00:27:17.070 --> 00:27:22.070 align:middle line:84%
>> Are there any craft that have
defensive shields that block

00:27:22.070 --> 00:27:23.720 align:middle line:84%
