00:27:23.720 --> 00:27:24.520 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yeah.

00:27:24.520 --> 00:27:26.870 align:middle line:84%
>> --block from a
missile coming in?

00:27:26.870 --> 00:27:28.310 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, absolutely.

00:27:28.310 --> 00:27:29.900 align:middle line:84%
The important
thing to understand

00:27:29.900 --> 00:27:33.230 align:middle line:84%
about such technology
is, so far, we

00:27:33.230 --> 00:27:35.900 align:middle line:84%
have not come to an
understanding of something

00:27:35.900 --> 00:27:38.810 align:middle line:84%
that is an ultimate defense
or an ultimate attack.

00:27:38.810 --> 00:27:41.600 align:middle line:90%
So you have levels.

00:27:41.600 --> 00:27:44.240 align:middle line:84%
We may have a
defense that's here.

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:46.790 align:middle line:84%
So anything that's
attacking here below

00:27:46.790 --> 00:27:48.030 align:middle line:90%
