00:27:48.030 --> 00:27:51.680 align:middle line:84%
But if something can
be considered here,

00:27:51.680 --> 00:27:53.728 align:middle line:84%
well, then that's
overcoming the defense,

00:27:53.728 --> 00:27:55.520 align:middle line:84%
and you need your
defense to go up to here.

00:27:55.520 --> 00:27:57.312 align:middle line:84%
So there's this constant
process that we're

00:27:57.312 --> 00:27:59.870 align:middle line:84%
going through that is every time
we come up against something

00:27:59.870 --> 00:28:03.500 align:middle line:84%
that's stronger than what we
came up with before, well,

00:28:03.500 --> 00:28:05.990 align:middle line:84%
then we adapt and come up
with better shielding, better

00:28:05.990 --> 00:28:08.780 align:middle line:84%
defense technology to
defend against that thing.

00:28:08.780 --> 00:28:11.150 align:middle line:84%
So we're in a constant
upgrading process.

00:28:11.150 --> 00:28:15.320 align:middle line:84%
>> Do they have special weapons
